OL,3,CJury told rape suspect followed Sikh
OL,4,Cwoman and attacked her in her own home
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,7,Fof a distressing nature
OL,9,FThe jury in the trial of a man charged
OL,10,Fwith rape and the racially-aggravated
OL,11,Fassault on a Sikh woman in Walsall,
OL,12,Fhas heard how he followed her home and
OL,13,Fbroke into her house to attack her.
OL,15,FJohn Ashby, who's 32, is accused of
OL,16,Fattacking the victim after travelling
OL,17,Fon the same bus as her.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
