OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776777070
OL,3,CJury told rape suspect followed Sikh
OL,4,Cwoman and attacked her in her own home
OL,6,FThe jury at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,7,Fheard how Mr Ashby followed a woman
OL,8,Ffrom Walsall town centre on a bus to
OL,9,Fthe Park Hall area, on the evening of
OL,10,F25th October 2025.
OL,12,FCCTV footage showed him getting off
OL,13,Fthe same bus as the woman. He followed
OL,14,Fher for around ten minutes, with some
OL,15,Fdistance between them.
OL,17,FShe did not know she was being
OL,18,Ffollowed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776777070
OL,3,CJury told rape suspect followed Sikh
OL,4,Cwoman and attacked her in her own home
OL,6,FHe was then seen loitering outside her
OL,7,Fhouse, where he found a stick around a
OL,8,Fmetre and a half long, which he put in
OL,9,Fhis clothes.
OL,11,FCCTV then picked up a scream from
OL,12,Finside the woman's house.
OL,14,FProsecuting Phil Bradley KC said the
OL,15,Fwoman heard a sound in her house, and
OL,16,Ftried to lock the bathroom door but it
OL,17,Fwas too late, as Mr Ashby had forced
OL,18,Fhimself in.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
