OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776777070
OL,3,CJury told rape suspect followed Sikh
OL,4,Cwoman and attacked her in her own home
OL,6,FThe jury heard he turned the lights
OL,7,Foff, struck the woman with the stick,
OL,8,Fput his hands around her neck to
OL,9,Fstrangle her, and poured hot water on
OL,10,Fher in the bathtub.
OL,12,FThe jury were told he believed the
OL,13,Fwoman was a Muslim, shouted racial
OL,14,Fslurs at her and raped her.
OL,16,FAround half an hour later, CCTV picked
OL,17,Fup Mr Ashby running from the house,
OL,18,Fand the woman screaming for help.
OL,20,FHe was arrested three days later.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
