PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776777070
OL,3,CJury told rape suspect followed Sikh
OL,4,Cwoman and attacked her in her own home
OL,6,FHe has been charged with rape,
OL,7,Fintentional strangulation, robbery as
OL,8,Fhe stole jewellery and a mobile phone
OL,9,Fas he left the house, and racially-
OL,10,Faggravated assault.
OL,12,FHe pleaded not guilty to all four
OL,13,Fcharges. The trial continues.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
